node.text: ‘Upload’ actress @andyallo got super creative in her kitchen for Cosmo’s ‘Stir Crazy’ challenge where she literally created her own berry lemonade from scratch. 🙌 (Mocktails are fun too!) LIKE WHAT?! 👀 We definitely suggest you try making this at home because it looks freakin’ fantastic. And be sure to stream her show ‘Upload’ streaming on Amazon Prime!

node.title: You're Gonna Be Obsessed with Andy Allo's Berry Lemonade Mocktail
